title: Lunchbox Gets The Shocker + Is Eddie Letting His Kids Do Something Inappropriate?

description:
Bobby brings back a segment called "Shocker Trivia" and Lunchbox is the first to play. Every time he misses an answer, he gets shocked by a dog shock collar. Also, Eddie's kids have been into some rap music that may not be suitable for their young ears!
